features: DURABLE TO USE: This alarm bell can be on for 30 hours, turn the battery upside down to turn on the light. When you need the light to shine, you only need to turn the upper battery over.
SENSITIVE AND QUICK: The bell of the alarm is connected by a precise and sensitive spring. Once a fish bites the hook, the bell can react quickly and send out a crisp sound to remind you.
FEATURES: The clip is solid and durable, without sliding rod phenomenon. The galvanized bell is crisp, can automatically alarm. The double hole design can insert the luminous stick.
APPLICABILITY: The clip size of the alarm is suitable for most fishing rods on the market, and the fishing bell is easy to carry, is very suitable for fishermen and fishing enthusiasts.
INSTALL: When you need to use the clip, turn out the light and take out the button battery inside. Then flip the battery and reinstall into the light. Tighten the light and will light up.
